=comment Package: Gdk4, C-Source: events
use v6.d;

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#--[Class Description]----------------------------------------------------------
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gdk4::Event
=head1 Description

Represents windowing system events.

In GTK applications the events are handled automatically by toplevel
widgets and passed on to the event controllers of appropriate widgets,
so using B<Gnome::Gdk4::Event> and its related API is rarely needed.

B<Gnome::Gdk4::Event> structs are immutable.

=begin comment

=head2 Example
# Example use of module Gnome::Gdk4::Event

=end comment

=end pod

